Apple and Major League Baseball this week <a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/07/apple-and-major-league-baseball-announce-august-friday-night-baseball-schedule/">announced</a> the August schedule for Friday Night Baseball, a weekly doubleheader of MLB games streamed on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/apple-tv/">Apple TV</a>+ throughout the 2025 regular game season.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/06/MLB-Friday-Night-Baseball-Feature.jpg" alt="" width="1960" height="1103" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1004669" /><br/>
Friday Night Baseball is included with an &zwnj;Apple TV&zwnj;+ subscription, at no additional cost. In the U.S., &zwnj;Apple TV&zwnj;+ costs &#36;9.99 per month or &#36;99 per year, and it is also included in all <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-one/">Apple One</a> subscription bundles with other Apple services.<br/>
<br/>
