Milwaukee Brewers at Cincinnati Reds<br/>
6:40 p.m.  ET<br/>
<br/>
Texas Rangers at Toronto Blue Jays<br/>
7:07 p.m. ET<br/>
<br/>
<strong>Friday, 8/22</strong><br/>
