Atlanta Braves at Philadelphia Phillies<br/>
6:45 p.m.  ET<br/>
<br/>
Baltimore Orioles at San Francisco Giants<br/>
10:15 p.m. ET</blockquote>Available in 60 countries, Apple says Friday Night Baseball provides enhanced production quality, expert commentary, no local broadcast restrictions, and more.<div class="linkback">Tags: <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-tv-plus/">Apple TV Plus</a>, <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/mlb/">MLB</a></div><br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/07/01/apple-tv-announces-mlb-schedule-for-august/">Apple TV+ Announces MLB Friday Night Baseball Schedule for August</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/apple-tv-announces-mlb-friday-night-baseball-schedule-for-august.2460005/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>